articles.title: Eminem’s ‘Houdini’ Unlocks No. 1 Debut on Billboard Global Charts - Billboard
articles.description: The song becomes the rapper’s first ruler on both the Global 200 and Global Excl. U.S.
articles.content: Eminem’s “Houdini” magically appears at No. 1 in its first week on both the Billboard Global 200 and Billboard Global Excl. U.S. charts. It becomes the rapper’s first leader on the lists, which began… [+3204 chars]
